etomica.atom

Class AtomTypeOriented

  • java.lang.Object
    • etomica.atom.AtomType
      • etomica.atom.AtomTypeOriented

  • public class AtomTypeOriented
extends AtomType
    Atom type for a sphere that has some feature depending upon an orientation coordinate. For example an orientational dependent potential may be attached to an otherwise spherical atom
